hi friends! doing something new today and showing off some posts from the Feeding a Broken Heart series! 👆🏼💕 it makes my heart so happy to see pictures of the food you're sharing with friends and family who are facing a loss, a breakup, a diagnosis... and the food you're making in honor of lost loved ones, including our precious baby Afton.
.

Here are some favorites from this week:
