hello SUGAR FREE JANUARY! ✌🏼 who’s ready?? for 30 days I’ll be eating real, delicious food and cutting out refined sugar and I’d love to have you join me! this is not a cleanse, not a detox, not a weight loss program. it’s not strict, not mean, not shaming. it’s just loads of good recipes that are made without refined sugar. you make your own sugar free plan - for example, with mine, I still eat lots of fruit, and the occasional piece of dark chocolate, and have a glass of weekend wine. to me, it’s all about long term sustainability, and balance, and true enjoyment of what I’m eating. ❤️✨
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
